headline.main: NINE ARMY FLIERS RESCUED IN PACIFIC; Navy Plane Alights on Rough Sea to Save Them -- Heroes of Dec. 7 Tell Stories AMERICA'S WOUNDED AND EVACUEES RETURN HOME FROM THE BATTLEGROUNDS OF HAWAII NINE ARMY FLIERS RESCUED IN PACIFIC

lead_paragraph: HONOLULU, Dec. 31 -- The rescue of nine Army fliers who had been forced down at sea was announced today by the Navy.
